    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
seas 5 to 8 feet.

* WHERE...Cape Mendocino to Pt Arena out 10 nm.

* WHEN...Until 11 AM PDT Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
