   <Snippet>Coastal Waters Forecast for the Northern Gulf of Alaska Coast
up to 100 nm out including Kodiak Island and Cook Inlet.

Wind forecasts reflect the predominant speed and direction
expected. Sea forecasts represent an average of the highest
one-third of the combined wind wave and swell height.

.TODAY...SW wind 20 kt. Seas 5 ft.
.TONIGHT...S wind 20 kt. Seas 5 ft. Rain.
.SAT...S wind 20 kt. Seas 8 ft. Rain.
.SAT NIGHT...S wind 25 kt. Seas 8 ft.
.SUN...S wind 25 kt. Seas 9 ft.
.MON...W wind 25 kt. Seas 10 ft.
.TUE...W wind 20 kt. Seas 5 ft.</Snippet>
